(1)
Shore Road, at Wakeman Place, showing the Owl's Head Observatory at right in the park.
October 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same; a view from the opposite direction, showing a plant of the Brooklyn Edison Co., at the left.
October 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3)
The same, at a later date showing Wakeman Place completed.
April 29, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
